report.name: AST005 - Patients on the asthma register
report.description: AST005: The contractor establishes and maintains a register of patients with asthma, aged 6 years or over, excluding patients with asthma who have been prescribed no asthma-related drugs in the preceding 12 months.

criterion.description: Patients Taking Asthma Treatment in last 12 months
